{"tid":1673401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Ideas are bulletproof] 加泰集會反映香港人根本冇信念","createTime":"2019-10-24T15:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T20:01:38.000Z","uid":22741,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"de872edf63673c527aec84369a54ecdd153b922a","tid":1673401,"uid":22741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:40:58.000Z","msg":"首先，留意到以下幾個acct 都係失敗主義者/分化撚<br />\n唔理佢地係唔係鬼<br />\n呢幾個一定要block柒佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eb1uVo3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEb1uVo3.png&h=bffd2271&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aAcem34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaAcem34.png&h=15873065&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1tbe6vM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1tbe6vM.png&h=d59158e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s5BVQXs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs5BVQXs.png&h=55abd207&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w16KKhu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw16KKhu.png&h=1642dcb9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PmsRphv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPmsRphv.png&h=4e3cc4a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UHQfQXw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUHQfQXw.png&h=4a738779&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Mazm4c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Mazm4c.png&h=a3efbf2a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X4ZTCCz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX4ZTCCz.png&h=4a98fc26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過左4個月，唔知大家仲記唔記得場運動既原意<br />\n<br />\n反極權，爭取屬於香港人既民主<br />\n<br />\n上面呢堆acct 一起底就睇到佢地有個風向<br />\n<br />\n就係反港獨 透過抹黑加泰獨立<br />\n<br />\n從而影響香港人爭取獨立既信念同信心<br />\n<br />\n雙普選係共產黨主權係冇可能可行<br />\n<br />\n你睇就連台灣 都俾人滲透曬<br />\n<br />\n冇論邊個當選 都只會繼續進行溫水煮蛙<br />\n<br />\n點解要撐加泰？<br />\n一方面要聲援被極權抗壓既加泰人<br />\n佢地面對著全世界既反對，都堅持對抗西班牙<br />\n點解佢地話要做新香港，唱香港國歌，正正相信香港人對民主自由 既價值既追求，係唔會受到任何利益影響<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一方面都加強既香港人自己對抗極權既信念<br />\n當你自己口口聲聲話要對抗極權，叫人幫你地手<br />\n其他地方有事，你為左一個人權法案為左利益就屈番加泰人係共狗？咁只係證明左你對自由根本冇追求<br />\n你追求既只係發泄自己既憤怒<br />\n你追求既只係出黎屌下黑警，屌下共狗<br />\n<br />\n今日出黎既一千幾百，我敢講絕對係700萬人當中立場最堅定<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立，係唯一出路。<br />\n<br />\n連香港獨立都唔敢講，你驚俾人dq 你？<br />\n而家唔係要叫你即刻拎把槍出黎打仗<br />\n係要透過不斷咁叫香港獨立，加強對香港獨立既信念同信心<br />\n如果你冇勇氣對抗極權，驚叫下會俾人拉既，咁你就不如繼續做港豬<br />\n如果你係真黃既，請堅持香港獨立<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命 唔係一個口號鳩叫咁簡單<br />\n背後係提醒香港人對獨立既需要同信念。"},{"pid":"63f930aede5941ae3a50907c6e1172e0d72ece2e","tid":1673401,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:41:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/itbR4in.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FitbR4in.jpg&h=bd7ae3e5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3b03c3a353e3447f50c7cd9c51061e053a9da511","tid":1673401,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:42:31.000Z","msg":"Ideas are bulletproof 只係冷氣軍師既口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec7b29b3b06067155c057459e6458ca13e6491f8","tid":1673401,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"de872edf63673c527aec84369a54ecdd153b922a","tid":1673401,"uid":22741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:40:58.000Z","msg":"首先，留意到以下幾個acct 都係失敗主義者/分化撚<br />\n唔理佢地係唔係鬼<br />\n呢幾個一定要block柒佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eb1uVo3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEb1uVo3.png&h=bffd2271&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aAcem34.png\" data-thumbnail-src