係提醒香港人對獨立既需要同信念。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:43:58.000Z","msg":"加油呀手足"},{"pid":"5b2e98c23277c2b497297de149be280e31b4656c","tid":1673401,"uid":22741,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:45:14.000Z","msg":"仲有頭兩個月當初一樣冇咩人權法<br />\n大家依然義無反顧咁出黎<br />\n點解而家會咁多分化<br />\n淨淨係五毛狗利用香港人對人權法案依賴既心態去叫人咩都唔做，攪散場運動<br />\n<br />\n唔好裝修，唔好舉港英旗，唔好攪黨鐵，唔好勇武，反港獨，反加泰<br />\n邊次唔係利用人權法案去煽動<br />\n希望大家俾d信心美國，俾d獨立思考<br />\n就算全香港人700萬人講香港獨立<br />\n國際輿論依然係企我地個邊"},{"pid":"0ec4acb3b87a93d23a6a6f083d36f08ba80b0afe","tid":1673401,"uid":283912,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:46:31.000Z","msg":"加油,繼續鞭繼續分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6320547cef6ddbf240023f8f4d848618d9907a1","tid":1673401,"uid":22741,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3b03c3a353e3447f50c7cd9c51061e053a9da511","tid":1673401,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:42:31.000Z","msg":"Ideas are bulletproof 只係冷氣軍師既口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:47:06.000Z","msg":"屌啦星班五毛狗 200人都講得出<br />\n香港獨立只係極少數分化撚都講得出<br />\n<br />\n真心膠唔該睇清佢地既面目<br />\n佢地只係每日涼緊冷氣袋住人民幣既大陸狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024f1c8d5c912edd5436db6d35ec477b0e1e9b0a","tid":1673401,"uid":207792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:47:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ca72278f6c2de493d6cec5f75fe08cc2ebde225d","tid":1673401,"uid":22741,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0ec4acb3b87a93d23a6a6f083d36f08ba80b0afe","tid":1673401,"uid":283912,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:46:31.000Z","msg":"加油,繼續鞭繼續分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24